  "detailed_description": "<h1>EarlyAccess</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/861050/extras/6db81c58f9023e45a24897b891a84f5d.avif?t=1723965813\" width=614 height=342 /></span><br><br>DRC Early Access is Live!<br><br>US Server Test Server is now open for 4000 Beta Testers. Register now and enter the hell's gate today. Follow link here: </p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>It’s all fun and games until someone ends up in Hell!<br><br>DemonsAreCrazy is an action-packed MOBA about a different type of electoral race, where demons vie for the title of President Satan. <br><br>Choose from 18 characters and gain notoriety by wreaking havoc and/or destroying everything in your path. Customize your demons’ skills, craft horrifically powerful equipment, and dive head-first into boss-hunts and quests – giving birth to the most evil, most deranged political party in history. Step right up – and enjoy Hell’s first election!",
  "about_the_game": "It’s all fun and games until someone ends up in Hell!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDemonsAreCrazy is an action-packed MOBA about a different type of electoral race, where demons vie for the title of President Satan. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nChoose from 18 characters and gain notoriety by wreaking havoc and/or destroying everything in your path. Customize your demons’ skills, craft horrifically powerful equipment, and dive head-first into boss-hunts and quests – giving birth to the most evil, most deranged political party in history. Step right up – and enjoy Hell’s first election!",
